com.azure.core.auth.credentials

Class MSIConfigurationForVirtualMachine

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.azure.core.auth.credentials.MSIConfigurationForVirtualMachine

  • public class MSIConfigurationForVirtualMachine
extends Object
    Defines the configuration to be used for retrieving access token from within a VM with user assigned or system assigned MSI enabled.
